@startuml
' Deliberation: the only pattern with a genuine sender-driven choice. The Reflector
' either continues (dispatch the Tool-Caller, loop) or converges (finalize). Palette:
' choice/critic=gold, loop=indigo, converge=green, divergence=red.
skinparam backgroundColor transparent
skinparam defaultFontName Inter
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor #e0e7ff
  BorderColor #3730a3
  FontColor #1e1b4b
}

[*] --> Reflect
state "μL: O→R:reflect_req" as Reflect
Reflect --> Choice : R→O : verdict
state Choice <<choice>> #fef9c3
Choice --> Act : **continue**
Choice --> Converged : **converged**
state "O→T:act_req · T→O:result" as Act #e0e7ff
Act --> Reflect : loop back to L
state "O→T:finish · T→O:final" as Converged #dcfce7
Converged --> [*]

note right of Converged #fee2e2
  spec: Tool-Caller produces the final answer.
  text impl stops at R→O:converged ⇒
  csm_validate_run reports Incomplete{T}
  (the divergence the observer surfaces)
end note
@enduml
